description: City Point three-bedroom condo was recently renovated (July 2024). It features a new white shaker cabinet/granite countertop kitchen with stainless steel appliances, a subway tile bathroom, new and re-finished floors, and a fresh coat of paint. This well-laid-out condo is a great investor unit or perfect for a first-time buyer with roommates. Its location, within steps of M Street beach, the Broadway shops & restaurants, and minutes to the Seaport/Financial District, makes it a contemporary gem with unparalleled convenience.
